{"tid":341091,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"撻朵勒索不成 黑幫男走夾唔抖","createTime":"2017-07-30T13:08:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-30T13:08:57.000Z","uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6645789eb3a786b14481c8b23af10acaadd16b0b","tid":341091,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T13:08:57.000Z","msg":"<strong>撻朵勒索不成 黑幫男走夾唔抖</strong><br />\n<br />\n即時突發  2017-07-30 05:11:44 HKT\t <br />\n         <br />\n大角嘴埃華街一間公司，昨晚約11時，一名男子突然走入，自稱三合會成員向49歲姓周女職員勒索。女職員不為所動，報警求助，男子立即逃去。案件由旺角警區刑事調查隊第四隊跟進，暫時無人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}